ou are stupid or your path just crosses with the problems’ path by luck! Nobody is sending you problems to test you! Stay loose and chuck out the irrational idea of ‘test’ at once!', 3701, 0), (55466, 'Grace is the best accessory that a woman can wear', 12556, 0), (55467, 'Being a dumb is better than being a dummy', 12557, 0), (55468, 'Science is good, is not God.', 4618, 0), (55469, 'The day you discover the GOD within, your quest to meet GOD outside stops!!!', 4632, 0), (55470, 'Just because the roads were bad in the past we drive slow but if we still continue the same way on the highway of Life, you can never ‘Accelerate', 4632, 0), (55471, 'Desire to dwell in a clean environment.', 2878, 0), (55472, 'If you think the world is a tough place, it time to change your lens!!!!', 4632, 0), (55473, 'You can only give and display what you have if you are frustrated with others you are quite a frustrating person and if you are loving others, you are a lovely person!', 4632, 0), (55474, 'Killing or eating animals is an act of beasts. Stirs within the devil. Sorry. It spurs evil. Thus is truth - at least the metaphysical.', 4618, 0), (55475, 'As per the law of karma, that which is your meat today, this dear beloved animal will make mincemeat of you tomorrow. In another birth.', 4618, 0), (55476, 'I am not mean I am just sarcastically humorous', 33, 0), (55477, 'All humans are rogues. Cured only by death.', 4618, 0), (55478, 'The river asked me who I was to be gazing so longingly into her curving body of cascading dreams and shifting beauty.', 12558, 0), (55479, 'Don''t spend your life wondering "what if" and worrying over something you have no control. What''s done is done. Looking backwards will cause you to miss out on new blessings ahead. Move on.', 2736, 0), (55480, 'In moments when you feel that life is unbearably heavy, surrender yourself to the circumstances for a while! When life hits you hard and makes you fall down, take a rest on the ground for a while! Momentaneous non-resistance will give you time to gather your strength!', 3701, 0), (55481, 'But one of the big lessons I have learned from my journey is you can''t please everyone, so don''t try.', 6614, 0), (55482, 'The longer you hold on to your anger, the more damage & harm it can do. But I think life should have given us someone who could understand every feeling we hide behind our smile. A best friend maybe.... Someone, you feel comfortable with.', 5598, 0), (55483, 'Our mind speak to our souls about the lifestyle we should have. Nobody can dictate our souls because we only have control of our own character and ambition.', 10314, 0), (55484, 'Envision life as you''re juggling 6 balls. The balls are called faith, work, family, health, friends, and integrity. But one day, you realize that work is a rubber ball. If dropped, it will bounce back. The other 5 balls faith, family, health, friends, & integrity are made of glass. If you drop one of these, it will be surely scuffed, nicked, or even shattered. Grasp this concept and you will have the beginnings of balance in your life.', 5610, 0), (55485, 'Life, life.', 5072, 0), (55486, 'If you don''t know what you want form life, everything will appear either as an obstacle or a burden. But one of the greatest lessons of history is that the whole world gets out of the way for people who know what they want or where they are going. Be assure, if you don''t know where you are going, you are lost.', 3409, 0), (55487, 'Some lessons are learnt the hard way, but worth it.', 5160, 0), (55488, 'In the struggle between yourself and the world, side with the world', 90, 0), (55489, 'But these were days of self-fulfillment, where settling for something that was not quite your first choice of a life seemed weak-willed and ignoble. Somewhere, surrendering to what seemed to be your fate had changed from being dignified to being a sign of your own cowardice.', 767, 0), (55490, 'Be the girl you want your daughter to be. Be the girl you want your son to date. Be classy, be smart, be real, but most importantly be nice.', 2736, 0), (55491, 'What are you doing with life God has given you?', 2878, 0), (55492, 'I wonder that if you keep growing and changing like you''re supposed to, if you always end up embarrassed about how stupid you used to be. Every year I realize how dumb I was the year before.', 349, 0), (55493, 'I had an enemy - myself. Getting rid of the ego-self, in came the Self. Now, here, there, everywhere is nothing else. Just One Self.', 4618, 0), (55494, 'Every man shall give account of his life to his Maker.', 2878, 0), (55495, 'How do you live thy sacred life?', 2878, 0), (55496, 'Love is a kind of insanity.', 2878, 0), (55497, 'It is fatal to forget the heavenly Father.', 2878, 0), (55498, 'Naked we were born, naked shall we return to grave. What then is the toil?', 2878, 0), (55499, 'The chase of the whirlwind is vanity.', 2878, 0), (55500, 'We shall know how to live better, if we read the Holy Bible.', 2878, 0);
